The roots of the Chebyshev polynomial $T_N(x)$ are
\begin{equation}
\xi_k = \cos\left(\frac{(2k + 1)\pi}{2N}\right), \quad k = 0, 1, \ldots, N-1.
\end{equation}
These are $N$ distinct real numbers in the interval $(-1, 1)$.
